    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) In nomine domini Dei eterni. Anno ab incarnatione domini nostri Iesu
                        Christi millesimo centesimo vigesimo tercio, de mense martii, inditione
                        quintadecirna. Constat nos <persName
                            key="#marriage #Roman #Venditio #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Forests #Witness"
                                ><name ref="Aderlatus">Haderlatus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#marriage #Roman #Venditio #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Forests #Witness"
                                ><name ref="Anstruda">Anestruda</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">iugales</rs> qui professi sumus lege vivere <rs
                            key="#Roman">Romana</rs> accepisemus sicuti et in presentia <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs> accepimus a vobis domnus <persName
                            key="#Priors #Monasteries" ref="#people/3509">Ubertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">prior</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Priors #Missus #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Forests #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancii Benedicti</orgName> et domnus
                            <persName key="#Missus"><name ref="Autecheri"
                            >Odogerius</name></persName> et domnus <persName key="#Missus"><name
                                ref="Dominicus/de Maringo">Dominicus</name></persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2932">Maringo</placeName>, <rs key="#Missus">legati</rs>
                        Sancti Benedicti in Pado Larone, <rs key="#Price">triginta libras
                            Mediolanensium monete</rs>, finitum pretiurn pro <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> cum <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Oil">olivis</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals">terra aratoria</rs> et
                        olivis seu <rs key="#Forests">saliciis</rs>, monte cum <rs key="#Forests"
                            >nemore</rs> atque omnia sibi pertinentia secundum mensure et coherentie
                        eius terrę quę <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">boni viri</rs> illius
                        patrie ibi invenire potuerint, et quantum mihi pertinet iure que iacet in
                        pertinentie <placeName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Houses"
                            ref="#places/258">Lazesi</placeName>, silicet in loco qui nominatur
                            <placeName ref="#places/258">Fabianus</placeName>. Coheret ei: a monte
                        via, a meridie et sera heredibus quondam <persName><name ref="Otto"
                                >Ottoni</name></persName> et <orgName>Sanctum Martinum
                            Lazesiensem</orgName> et <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/90">Sanctum
                            Zenonem <placeName ref="#places/59">Veronensem</placeName></orgName>
                        atque heredibus quondam <persName><name ref="Dominicus"
                            >Dominici</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Maginfredus"
                                >Mainfredus</name></persName>, a mane <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">Sancti Petri et Sancti Iuliani</orgName>, si et
                        sibique alii sunt coerentes. Que autem ista terra cum vineis et olivis et
                        salitiis et nemore et pratis una cum accessionibus suis et bosculo et capula
                        et ingressibus seu cum superioribus et inferioribus qualiter supra legitur
                        in integrum ab hac die vobis cui supra domno Uberto et domno Odogerio et
                        domno Dominico, legati monasterii Sancti Benedicti, pro isto pretio
                        vendimus, tradimus, emancipamus, nulli alii vendita, donata, alienata,
                        obnoxiata vel tradita nisi vobis legatis Sancti Benedicti, ut fatiatis
                        exinde a presenti die vos et vestros successores vel qui pro tempore erint
                        constituti in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Sancti Benedicti sine
                        ulla contradictione mea vel meorum heredum. Quidem spondeo atque promitto me
                        ego qui supra Adherlatus una cum meis heredibus vobis cui supra missi Sancti
                        Benediciti vel vestris successoribus aut cui vos daretis ista encione
                        qualiter supra legitur in integrum ab omni homine defensare promittimus;
                        quod si defendere non potuerimus vobis <rs key="#Penalty">induplabimus</rs>
                        sicut ius est in consimilem locum, et nec nobis ex ipso precio aliquit re
                        debere diximus. Actum in loco Laçesi, silicet in <rs key="#Houses">domo</rs>
                        <persName key="#Houses #Witness #Venditio #parentOf"><name
                                ref="Bonusvicinus">Bonivicini</name></persName> feliciter. Signum ++
                        Aderlati et Anestuda iugales qui hanc <rs key="#Venditio">cartulam
                            vendicionis</rs> rogarunt et suprascriptum precium acceperunt ut supra.
                        Signum suprascripti <persName key="#Witness #Venditio #Roman"><name
                                ref="Hugo">Ugonis</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio #Roman"><name ref="Sinicus"
                            >Senichonis</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio #Roman"><name ref="Raginbaldus"
                            >Rambaldi</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2942"
                            >Bardolino</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness #Venditio #Roman"
                                ><name ref="Amizo">Amiçoni</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio #Roman"><name ref="Oliverius"
                            >Oliverii</name></persName> vivencium lege Romana uius facti testium.
                        Signum ++++++ suprascripti <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Maginfredus">Maifredi</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Beneventus"
                                >Beneventi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"
                                ><name ref="Ampertus">Amperti</name></persName> et Bonivicini et <rs
                            key="#childOf">filius</rs> eius <persName
                            key="#childOf #Witness #Venditio"><name ref="David"
                            >Daviti</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Rainerius">Rainerii</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Otto">Otonis</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Martinus"
                            >Martini</name></persName> testium. (S.) Ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Writer #Venditio"><name ref="Bardolinus"
                            >Bardolinus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> rogatu <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Albericus">Alberici</name></persName> notarii et monachorum
                        hanc cartulam vendicionis <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et complevi
                        feliciter. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
